{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "story_excu_set_1", "eventName": "送葬人", "entryType": "NONE", "storyCode": null, "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "送葬人", "storyInfo": "針對其在任務中表現出的異常，第五廳樞機與送葬人進行了一場談話。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g12_laterano_office", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$tech_intro", "key": "$tech_loop", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "姓名，費德里科·吉亞洛。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。目前生理指標一切正常，沒有不適情況。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隨時可以接受問詢。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是談話，不是問詢？明白，我會在我所知範圍內如實回答所有提問。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請說。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.3, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不是我第一次見到這個說話一板一眼的新人。"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "中庭公證所上一年招收了三名見習執行者，其中兩名很遺憾最終未能加入我們。"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其中一人沒能通過實習期的考核，另一人忽然發現還是繼承家裡的甜品店更適合自己，於是在轉正前一天遞交辭呈。"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後剩下的，就是這名叫費德里科的年輕人。"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "費德里科，我希望可以再聽你敘述一遍你的任務經過。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line31"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明白。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "本次任務由中庭公證所派發，契約人為一位已故拉特蘭公民。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "契約人在遺囑中寫明，希望公證所為他尋找失散在外的後人，並將其帶回拉特蘭。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因遺囑執行難度較高，本次委託由兩名執行者共同完成。我已將遺囑繼承人帶回，其身份已經確認。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "報告中提到，你的搭檔在任務途中犧牲。;報告中提到，你本人在行動中受了重傷。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line43", "option2": "line48"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line53"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "執行者貝托尼在行動過程中殉職。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "2"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line53"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "記錄無誤。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "衝擊傷三處，穿刺傷一處，均不致命，已接受治療。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": true}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在本次任務執行期間，我與執行者貝托尼依據公民遺囑，進入玻利瓦爾邊境地帶尋找其遺囑繼承人。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "該地區目前正處於戰亂狀態，缺乏穩定的社會秩序。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遺囑繼承人被捲入當地武裝衝突中，這對我們完成任務造成了一定阻礙。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在尋人途中，我們共遭遇三次混戰，遺囑繼承人一度被挾持，執行者貝托尼因此身負重傷。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "執行者貝托尼傷勢很重，以當時的醫療條件很難進行有效救助。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其本人對自己的情況做出了判斷，並制定了下一步的行動方案。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在他的計劃裡，他將成為誘餌吸引各方注意，而我在掩護下行動，確保遺囑繼承人的人身安全。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在當時的情況下，這確實是合理的安排。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.3, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "關於任務的敘述，到此為止沒有半句謊言。"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的執行者會被派往最危險的地帶執行任務，因公殉職也並非個例。"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是費德里科的情況稍顯特殊。"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "負責與其對接的同僚顯然有些憂慮，因此我才站在這裡，向這個年輕人問話。"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "但是你並沒有按照他的計劃行動。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line81"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恕我直言，執行者貝托尼的計劃與我們需要執行的遺囑有衝突之處。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遺囑中除明確要求公證所代為找回後人，將其護送回到拉特蘭以外，還有其他申請條目。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“希望所有拉特蘭人終歸故土。”", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是他附加在遺囑最後的申請。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然公證所已經受理其遺囑，確保其全部內容得到執行就是我的工作。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.3, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“希望所有拉特蘭人終歸故土。”"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是個多美好的期許。但我能說，它是需要被執行的遺囑的一部分嗎？"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看著面前這雙眼。"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它們堅硬，平靜，沒有絲毫漣漪。"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我真希望我能夠透過這片淡藍色，看出一點什麼來。"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "執行者貝托尼的計劃中，對其自身的規劃並不明確。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "玻利瓦爾邊境局勢混亂，各方人員混雜，其中並不乏對拉特蘭懷有敵意的勢力。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這樣的情況下，我無法聽從安排，帶遺囑繼承人先行離開。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請見諒。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "你很清楚你將貝托尼背回拉特蘭時，他是什麼狀態吧？", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line112"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。我很清楚。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "執行者貝托尼在我們嘗試脫圍時，已經基本失去行動能力，因此之後的安排中由我背負其行動。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "成年男子的體重尚在可承受的負重範圍內，並沒有太大問題。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當時他的失血量已超過人體可承受界限，體溫下降到危險狀態，其本人很快失去意識。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "脫離玻利瓦爾邊境當天，執行者貝托尼確認死亡。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.3, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這絕不是我第一次耳聞同僚的離去。也不會是最後一次。"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不禁思考，如果死者當真有知，貝托尼現在會怎麼想？"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他會願意見到這個年輕人，為將自己帶回拉特蘭而身受重傷，甚至險些送命嗎？"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "貝托尼一定不同意你這麼做。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line133"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "執行者貝托尼確實表示反對。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但他無法給其反對附加合理的解釋，因此我選擇維持我的判斷。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "結合任務與當時情況，契約人的遺囑執行為當時的最高優先順序，執行者貝托尼的個人意願優先度較低。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如有特殊情況，我會列入考慮。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.3, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是我瞭解到的，關於費德里科·吉亞洛的另一特殊之處——"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個年輕人在共感能力上有所缺失。"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在此之前我們的判斷是，這種缺失並不會影響其作為執行者的工作。"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是現在看來，或許我需要重新對這一結論進行評判。"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "費德里科，難道你認為貝托尼的意願並不重要？;或許你要嘗試站在貝托尼的角度來考慮他那時的心情。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line153", "option2": "line156"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line159"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我尊重執行者貝托尼的意願。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "2"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line159"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恕我直言，我不明白這樣做的意義。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": true}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "執行者貝托尼是本次任務的參與成員之一，身為執行者，確保契約人的遺囑順利執行是我們共同的意願。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這一點上我不認為存有異議。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.3, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我開始想要歎氣了。"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "貝托尼最後想要以自己為誘餌，所圖為何呢？"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "眼前的年輕人卻反而衝入混戰，差一點就要付出昂貴的代價，帶著滿身的傷痕也要將貝托尼帶回......"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他是否當真毫不在意？"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他是否當真完全無法理解......貝托尼最後的那丁點期望？"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "費德里科，你能明白我現在的情緒嗎？;費德里科，你是否真的完全不懂情感？", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line176", "option2": "line188"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line200"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.3, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "面前的年輕人沒有說話。"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他注視著我，像是在判斷什麼。但是判斷什麼呢？"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "忽然，他有了動作。"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費德里科拿起一支筆，在桌面上的白紙上畫下了什麼。"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他畫了一個圓。"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您的情緒代表悲傷。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "2"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line200"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.3, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "面前的年輕人沒有說話。"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他注視著我，像是在思考什麼。"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "忽然，他有了動作。"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費德里科拿起一支筆，在桌面上的白紙上畫下了什麼。"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他畫了一個方形。"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這場談話中存有質疑。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": true}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在剛才您對我的詢問中，包含有試探、疑惑、悲傷以及其他多種情感。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.3, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "年輕的執行者在紙上畫下了更多線條。"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不明白情感的成因，也難以理解情感對人的意義，但我能夠理解這一結果。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不同的情感可以被線條替代，直線與曲線構成不同的圖案，這對我很有幫助。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "由於天生的生理缺陷，我無法如多數同胞一般與人共感。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這並不會對我在公證所的任職造成影響。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會完成交給我的委託。如有必要，我會去理解契約人的情感。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.3, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費德里科說到這裡，忽然停頓了片刻。"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的心情此時已因為他的回答而大有改變，這個年輕人卻說出了更加出乎所有人意料的話。"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "關於執行者貝托尼殉職的後續處理，我已向公證所提交了遺囑執行申請。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在執行最終行動之前，貝托尼曾向我提及：", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“如果這次能活著回去，我一定要參加大教堂前那家冰淇淋店的十球挑戰。”", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“要是運氣差回不去，那就委託費德里科你幫我吃他個一百球吧！”", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——以上即是執行者貝托尼的口述遺囑。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.3, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......這或許只是貝托尼的自嘲，或是一個玩笑。"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我終於忍不住打斷費德里科的話。"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他畫下的那些線條組成種種幾何圖形，有序地排列在紙上，看在我眼中卻毫無規律可言。"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我忍不住猜測，這其中是否有一個圖形，正屬於說出這些話語時的貝托尼？"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "樞機閣下，我有能力判別資訊的真實與否。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "儘管我無法與他共感，但我有類似的經驗，能夠判斷說話者是否確有此意。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因接受錯誤的訊號而導致誤解的情況少有發生。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.3, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費德里科從始至終神色平靜，任誰也會覺得這是個冰冷的、無情的人。"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幾分鐘前，我尚在判斷共感能力的缺失是否會對他在公證所的工作造成影響。"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，我已開始為這個年輕人的表現歎息。"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我問自己，費德里科·吉亞洛確實有所缺陷，但這又如何呢？"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道因為有缺陷，就能說他是一個不通情感，思維機械，無法感受的人嗎？"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "這種透過線條解讀情感的方式也是你天生就領悟的嗎？", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line260"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，是我的雙親教會我使用這種方法。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.3, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個年輕人首次在問答中有了遲疑。"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看到他在說話的同時，手又動了起來，在那張白紙上畫出了更多的圖形。"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這一次我不必，也不應該開口詢問其含義。"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們曾是戍衛隊特勤隊成員，後轉調公證所成為執行者，在執行任務過程中殉職。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "令我能夠理解情感是他們遺囑的一部分，我目睹他們的死亡，並在那時首次嘗試解讀。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遺憾、不捨。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "與執行者貝托尼的情況有類似的部分。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您的情緒再次有所變化。為什麼？", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.3, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我無法回答這個問題。"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我確信在經歷多年的職業生涯之後，我已不會再輕易將情緒向外展露。"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這個年輕人卻說得如此篤定，毫不懷疑。"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "身為中庭公證所的執行者，我們比其他拉特蘭人要更容易見到人生百態，從生者到死者我們都要與之往來。"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從這種意義上來說，費德里科或許才是我們之中，真正毫無雜念的那一個。"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想......他確實會是一名合格的送葬人。"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "感謝你回答了我的所有疑問。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line297"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 298, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "費德里科，接下來你有什麼打算？", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line301"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然缺乏正式的申請手續，僅為當事人口述，但執行者貝托尼的遺囑有另一名執行者為其見證。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這樣的情況下，我認為可以將他的口述當作正式遺囑看待。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因此，我會申請為其執行遺囑。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#2"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.3, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說到這裡，年輕的執行者頭一次神色微動。"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他略微皺起眉。"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#2"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我已申請購買一百個冰淇淋球的執行經費。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#2"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不論如何......", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_279_excu_4#1"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會完成生者與死者交予我的囑託。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4#1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}